WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
narrator: a brand-new linux host joins an existing OctraVPN tailnet.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:12.000
narrator: the operator-supplied preauth key is already on the clipboard.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:22.000
narrator: install stock tailscale from the distro package manager.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:30.000
narrator: no octravpn binary is required — the plane is Tailscale-wire.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:40.000
narrator: tailscale up points at the operator login-server URL.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:50.000
narrator: the preauth key is consumed exactly once.

00:00:50.000 --> 00:01:00.000
narrator: the host is issued a 100.64.x.x tailnet IP.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:10.000
narrator: tailscale status lists every peer the operator authorised.

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:20.000
narrator: a ping to a peer confirms WireGuard is carrying traffic.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:30.000
narrator: the linux host is now a first-class tailnet member.
